             sworn. - Q. You are assistant shopman to the assistant of Mr. Powdich? - A. The prisoner came in and asked me for some<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="180504240059"></xptr>print; I shewed them a great number, I saw 
               <persName id="t18050424-70-person707">
